Hi Silas,

Following your phone call of this morning I called Jean-Fran=E7ois Arteau t=
o=20
know more about the possibility to hire a lawyer for the NRBHSS in the=20
Nunavik Regional Government (NRG) file for its eventual implementation.

Here is what I understood from my conversation with Jean-Frna=E7ois:

1. Recently, Pita recommended to Alasie, that the NRBHSS should hire a=20
lawyer in the NRG file since we are the only public organization to be=20
amalgamated that does not have a full time one.

2. It is up to the NRBHSS to have one or not.

3. Such lawyer would mainly be advising the NRBHSS during the transition=20
period (of 2 years) making sure that the amalgamation is done in=20
accordance with the "Final Agreement" and its subsequent Quebec Government =

relative legislation.

